  "about_sharda": "рҹҺ“ <b>Sharda University Uzbekistan</b>\n<i>A trusted step toward international education</i>\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n<b>Sharda University Uzbekistan</b> is an international private university located in Andijan, offering modern education, a strong academic environment, and global opportunities for students.\n\nEstablished under the Presidential Decree <b>PQ-4278</b> dated <b>10 April 2019</b>, the university stands out for its future-focused programs and international academic approach.\n\n<u>Key advantages:</u>\nвҖў modern and in-demand academic programs\nвҖў international learning environment\nвҖў opportunity to continue studies at overseas campuses\nвҖў a strong foundation for career and professional growth\n\n<i>вҖңThe world is here! Where are you?вҖқ</i>\n\nвңЁ <b>Start building your future with Sharda today.</b>",
  "contact_sharda": "рҹ“Қ <b>Sharda University Uzbekistan вҖ” Contact Information</b>\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\nрҹҸӣ <b>Address:</b>\n73, Babur Avenue, Andijan, Uzbekistan, 170100\n\nвҳҺпёҸ <b>Phone numbers:</b>\nвҖў <code>+998 90 527 12 34</code>\nвҖў <code>+998 90 529 12 34</code>\nвҖў <code>+998 95 420 09 09</code>\n\nрҹ“§ <b>Email:</b>\n<a href=\"mailto:admission@shardauniversity.uz\">Contact via email</a>\n\nрҹҢҗ <b>Official website:</b>\n<a href=\"https://www.shardauniversity.uz\">Official Sharda University Uzbekistan website</a>\n\nрҹ“ұ <b>Social media:</b>\nвҖў <a href=\"https://t.me/shardauniversityuz\">Telegram</a>\nвҖў <a href=\"https://instagram.com/shardauniuz\">Instagram</a>\nвҖў <a href=\"https://facebook.com/shardauniversity.uz\">Facebook</a>\nвҖў <a href=\"https://youtube.com/@shardauniuz\">YouTube</a>\n\nв„№пёҸ <i>Contact us for more information about admissions, programs, and student life.</i>",
  "faculty_info_sharda": "рҹ“ҳ <b>Sharda University Uzbekistan вҖ” Academic Programs</b>\n<i>BachelorвҖҷs and MasterвҖҷs programs</i>\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n<b>рҹҺ“ BachelorвҖҷs programs:</b>\n\nвҖў <b>Computer Science and Engineering</b>\nArtificial Intelligence and Machine Learning, Information Technologies, Cyber Security\n<i>Tuition: 20,240,000 UZS</i>\n\nвҖў <b>Business Administration</b>\nInternational Business\n<i>Tuition: 18,975,000 UZS</i>\n\nвҖў <b>Economics and Finance</b>\n<i>Tuition: 18,469,000 UZS</i>\n\nвҖў <b>Applied English</b>\n<i>Tuition: 17,710,000 UZS</i>\n\n<b>рҹҺ“ MasterвҖҷs programs:</b>\n\nвҖў <b>Master of Business Administration</b>\n<i>Tuition: 15,180,000 UZS</i>\n\nвҖў <b>Master of Technology in Computer Science and Engineering</b>\n<i>Tuition: 13,915,000 UZS</i>\n\nвңЁ <i>Modern education, career-oriented programs, and international opportunities вҖ” all in one place.</i>"
